{"tid":445191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★IT=下賤！捐電腦冇電線被嫌棄  \"虧你捐得出呀！！\"","createTime":"2017-10-23T07:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T15:41:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8af6952138bcd568decc6c8e0a6fd720417b74b3","tid":445191,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"有熱心人捐舊電腦予教會反被人鬧？有網民近日於社交群組「免『廢』島Free Island」聲稱代朋友發貼，直指一名捐舊電腦予教會的男子為「咁差嘅捐贈者」。貼文惹起網民熱議，其後發貼者急急刪文。<br />\n<br />\n原貼指，該套電腦是為某教會所徵，不過收到後一看，發現電腦竟然沒有「D drive」；而電腦螢幕屬「無座，不能自企」；鍵盤更為「跛腳」；而全套舊電腦更沒有附設電源線，令發貼者不禁大呻：<span style=\"color: red;\">「e(呢)位先生虧你捐得出呀！！」更外加兩個嬲嬲符號。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171023/bkn-20171023141747430-1023_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171023%2Fbkn-20171023141747430-1023_00822_001.html&d=1lmE1RvqZIO5N38ZfiZK04zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b9d3305b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171023/bkn-20171023141747430-1023_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"dd76b0b1bd97ff29d346d63d4b92c8da5ba400ee","tid":445191,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T07:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fd4e6d5658e1e8411841476cff7f042d0b578a","tid":445191,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T07:06:52.000Z","msg":"IT=虧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6e08d7e5c0f34ec6aa208c294f431625c1d353","tid":445191,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T07:08:51.000Z","msg":"唔行linux都唔好意思捐俾人啦"},{"pid":"25c5db7ebfaf11eeb21560b5